<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gird2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gird,</orth> vb. tr. and intr. to quiz, to reflect on: <cit><quote>men of all sorts take a pride to g. at me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he will not spare to g. the gods,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.260" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 260</bibl></cit>.
